WEBVTT

1
00:34:18.600 --> 00:34:21.010 
很难不去蹭脏他现在那白净的一身
Hard not to rub it on his clean, white shirt now.

2
00:34:25.740 --> 00:34:27.820 
还记得分析师沃伦·杰芬吗
Remember Warren Jaffin, the analyst?

3
00:34:29.030 --> 00:34:29.930 
记得
Yeah.

4
00:34:30.490 --> 00:34:31.470 
前途无量
Bright guy?

5
00:34:32.270 --> 00:34:33.250 
他很灵光
That kid was sharp.

6
00:34:33.250 --> 00:34:34.420 
该聘用他吗
Employable?

7
00:34:35.150 --> 00:34:36.340 
他确实不错  可以用
Real sharp, yeah.

8
00:34:36.340 --> 00:34:39.110 
他对年终奖不满  然后就走了
Then he balked at his bonus one year and got popped.

9
00:34:39.340 --> 00:34:41.700 
转身就在一家大银行拿到了一份工作
He got another job right away at a huge bank...

10
00:34:41.700 --> 00:34:43.580 
一年底薪三百万
$3 million a year, guaranteed.

11
00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:45.070 
只是  阿克斯听说
Only, word got back to Axe

12
00:34:45.070 --> 00:34:47.290 
沃伦在面试的时候说了他坏话
that Warren had bad mouthed him in the interview...

13
00:34:47.290 --> 00:34:49.430 
说阿克斯对他很吝啬
Said Axe wasn't generous with him.

